  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Emberfly</strong> is a first-person single-player horror game set in Korea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a way to escape from a dream that feels real but isn't.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-person horror</strong> - Single player in first-person perspective.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration and puzzles</strong> - Find hidden clues and solve simple puzzles (easy).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chase scenes</strong> - Run away to avoid being caught.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime </strong>- The first playtime is about 30-60 minutes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple endings</strong> – There are 3 endings.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, you wake up in an empty school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have no idea why you're here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's nighttime and the lights are off, so everything is dark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I don't know why, but luckily I have a flashlight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to find a way out of here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Icons by Icons8</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Emberfly</strong> is a first-person single-player horror game set in Korea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a way to escape from a dream that feels real but isn't.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-person horror</strong> - Single player in first-person perspective.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration and puzzles</strong> - Find hidden clues and solve simple puzzles (easy).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chase scenes</strong> - Run away to avoid being caught.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime </strong>- The first playtime is about 30-60 minutes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple endings</strong> – There are 3 endings.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, you wake up in an empty school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have no idea why you're here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's nighttime and the lights are off, so everything is dark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I don't know why, but luckily I have a flashlight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to find a way out of here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Icons by Icons8</p>",
